title: Bobby Gets Into Trouble At Therapy + Raymundo Picks His Final Groomsman + Lunchbox Calls To Rent Out A Movie Theater

description:
Bobby said he got in trouble in therapy yesterday after talking about work. Kane Brown told us last week that apparently Luke Bryan buys out the entire theater for a movie showing. Lunchbox called movie theaters to see how much it would be to rent out the entire theater. Raymundo reveals the 5th groomsman in his wedding. Also, Amy’s son mooned everyone on her live-stream last night.
